source.name: ENERGY STAR Certified Water Heaters
source.description: Certified models meet all ENERGY STAR requirements as listed in the Version 2.0 ENERGY STAR Program Requirements for Water Heaters that are effective as of July 1, 2013. A detailed listing of key efficiency criteria are available at http://www.energystar.gov/index.cfm?c=water_heat.pr_crit_water_heaters

datasets.name: ENERGY STAR Certified Water Heaters
datasets.description: This document describes how to use the API for ENERGY STAR  Certified Water Heaters.
